dreisoft.tresos.generator.ng.api.cds.ctypes
Interface IMemberSorter

All Known Implementing Classes:
AlignmentMemberSorter, SizeMemberSorter
public interface IMemberSorter

Implement this interface to change the natural order of the members of structs. The sorter instance must be assigned to a struct using Struct.setMemberSorter(IMemberSorter) to take effect.

Method Detail

sort

java.util.List<CType> sort(java.util.List<CType> members)
Sorts the given list of members.

Parameters:
members - The members in their natural order, never null.
Returns:
The given members in a sorted order. The resulting list must contain each member of the given members list. It is not allowed to modify the members in any way.
